hwmon: cix-fan: add fail-closed EC fan diagnostics

Probe optional read-only ACPI methods for target RPM, raw measured-RPM
bytes, and auto/manual mode readback. Expose fan1_input, fan1_fault,
and fan1_target only after their corresponding probe returns a defensible
value. Preserve both possible byte orders for the EC memory-map RPM and
decline to expose it when the live value is ambiguous.

The AML transport methods are supplied by the accompanying ORIONO6 table
upgrade; firmware without them retains the existing PWM-only interface.

